essage.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"The Prince andPrincess\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"Walesjoined up withSnoop Doggto\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"their congratulations\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"GBat\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympicsvia\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"a star-studded video message\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Describing the competitors as \\\"an inspiration to us all\\\", William and Kate released the celebrity-filled clip ahead ofthe closing ceremony at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999965188125085, \"rank\": 3.481289491836644e-05, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 730, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competitors\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspiration\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"William\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"the celebrity-filled clip\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"ofthe closing ceremony\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The King and the prime minister are also among those who have sent their congratulations to the athletes, withCharles similarly calling them \\\"an inspiration\\\"andSir Keir Starmerpraising them for inspiring a new generation.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The King\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"the prime minister\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"their congratulations\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"withCharles\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspiration\\\"andSir Keir\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"a new generation\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"William and Kate appeared in their video, with a compilation of messages from celebrities, including Snoop Dogg and David Beckham.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999965188125085, \"rank\": 3.481289491836644e-05, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Beckham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Beckham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Beckham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Beckham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"William\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"their video\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"a compilation\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"messages\", \"from\"