le\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3959628960825116e-17, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \", congratulations\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"William then added: \\\"Well done on all you have achieved, you have been an inspiration to us all.\\\"\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"William\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspiration\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Beckham said: \\\"Hey Team GB, we are so proud of you.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Beckham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3049176540547333e-16, \"text\": \"Beckham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Beckham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Beckham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations.\\\"\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Congratulations\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the others who featured in the video include former swimmer Rebecca Adlington, former track and field athlete Dame Jessica Ennis-Hill, former middle distance runner Dame Kelly Holmes, presenter and author Greg James and TV presenter Emma Willis.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Adlington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca Adlington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q1084340